{"tid":149201,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你班肥婆唔好再自欺欺人話重骨架","createTime":"2017-03-09T06:17:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T14:56:28.000Z","uid":86038,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"476b9a527444101507b7feb9920796bee4e42c63","tid":149201,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:17:22.000Z","msg":"肥，主要係你食多、訓多、懶得多，<br />\n啲肥婆成日話自己骨架大、喝水易肥，<br />\n真係人唔笑狗都吠。<br />\n<br />\n人由全身有大約206塊骨頭組成，所有骨頭佔身體既重量為10~20%<br />\n<br />\n骨頭佔你只不過最多20%，單單果20%你就話認命，放棄減肥？你唔係懶可以話你咩？<br />\n<br />\n再講，歐洲、美洲既女性高又高過你，大又大過你，區區果150身高你個骨架可以重得去邊。好多外國既女性身高170、180、甚至190大有人在。<br />\n<br />\n點解人地170cm、120lb，你就150cm、120kg呀？點解人地均勻發展，你就向橫發展呀？點解人地飲食文化周圍都係Pizza、Burger、Coca Cola，你就唔食 芥蘭、生菜、生果呀？<br />\n<br />\n你唔好同我講話你骨骼密度高、骨頭大之類、就算矮過人都重過人，通通都係籍口！<br />\n論你骨頭再大、密度再高都好，都唔係你成為肥婆既主要原因。<br />\n<br />\n因為世上重骨架既人只可以得佢一個有資格講&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/wlkphbyi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fwlkphbyi&h=d5cbb975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯！就係盧根！全身骨骼經過改造，而身體係由超高密度既亞德曼金屬組成。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0ag5mry3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0ag5mry3&h=ad51c3ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上狼人一過機場已經會俾成班機場特警圍住。你班肥婆如果個骨架真係由亞德曼金屬組成。我真係開心都嚟唔切呀！立即打俾X教授同佢講揾到大批變種人，叫盧根唔洗擔心同失望，因為佢喺香港有好多個女呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lk5cpiqr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flk5cpiqr&h=7bfaf49a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8f14afdb68b32376d091ab655eb0aa3b6b1a7f3","tid":149201,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"推俾班Xmen睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ee56fa9c4b5f0510e48d858d17e4e6974136f7","tid":149201,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/imn0skhl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fimn0skhl&h=8d0b6dd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"038397dab9d35e9f243942957356ffa730e18578","tid":149201,"uid":77697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有數據支持又有狼人<br />\n高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94565df1ba4da700cd76ff568741232397922cda","tid":149201,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">對唔住我會努力減肥</span>"},{"pid":"0a854cb93804dcacdb1d5d992367e89ee992ffea","tid":149201,"uid":86038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">對唔住我會努力減肥</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥婆唔係最重要 最重要係減走自欺欺人既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4c2a3036850c433584858a74d477cb331649ea","tid":149201,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"禾喜歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045ed4472774f1d26d0ae62685e7e4247